          <li>All MPA logos, trademarks, and content are the property of Malaysia Pickleball Association.</li>
          <li>Players may not use MPA intellectual property without written permission.</li>
          <li>Any photos or videos taken during MPA events may be used for promotional purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Liability and Insurance</h2>
        <h3>8.1 Assumption of Risk</h3>
        <p>By participating in pickleball activities, you acknowledge that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pickleball involves inherent risks of injury.</li>
          <li>You participate at your own risk and assume full responsibility for any injuries.</li>
          <li>MPA is not liable for injuries, accidents, or damages that may occur during participation.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>8.2 Insurance</h3>
